Package entity

Class Branch

java.lang.Object
entity.Branch
public class Branch extends Object
Branch class is used to store the information of a branch, including branchName, location, staffQuota, mgrQuota, numStaff, numManager, staffList, menuItems, orders.
Since:
2024-04-26
Version:
